1. Instalar un framework (express)
    npm init -y
    npm install dotenv eslint eslint-config-airbnb eslint-config-airbnb-base eslint-plugin-import eslint-plugin-security nodemon --save-dev
    npm install express --save
    
2. Crear un servidor web :8000
    
3. API REST
    
    app.get('/api/pokemons', (req, res, next) => {
